    ## BROKEN! Black holes do not properly suck non-player objects :(
    ## Bug registered at: https://github.com/artemis-sbs/LegendaryMissions/issues/344

    ## Since that's broke, I'm freeking going to hand-make an accretion disc!!! But damn, this is a lot of work!

    ## NORTH TAIL (Removed closest nebula to reduce density)
