    ## Update the Science scan info for Gaia BH3 (weirdly this block of code needs a double-Return at the end to work, not sure why)
    //enable/science if has_roles(SCIENCE_SELECTED_ID, "bbh")
    //science if has_roles(SCIENCE_SELECTED_ID, "bbh") 
    + "scan":
        <scan>
            % Gaia BH3 is a VERY dangerous black hole. It has a mass approximately 33 times the mass of the Earth's Sun. It is currently drawing in super-heated gas, creating a bright accretion disc that is detectable from a vast distance.


